                <para styleclass="Notes"><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">Note: </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">When you have a single segment and need it to be a constant velocity, you can also use a </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Gearing FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">, and use Gearing as Ratio radio-button.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Enter 360 as the Input Pulley parameter, and the End-Position as the Output-Pulley parameter.</text></para>
